y 85 percent so that's huge right you re 20 times more likely to die with a head injury we can fix ruptured spleens we can fix ruptured diaphragms we can fix broken legs we can fix broken arms we have nothing to offer the brain we can fix everything else except the brain x needs iframe support parking & transportation services is located at 340 bonair siding stanford ca 94305 7255 hours monday friday 7 30 am 5 pm phone 650.723 9362 fax 650.724 8676 email transportation stanford edu site map land buildings & real estate home bewell stanford stanford home
